# Local Cloudflare Workers secrets for `npm run preview` (OpenNext).
# Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in what you want. All optional — the app runs without these.
#
# Server-only key used by /api/generate-kit. In production set it with:
#   npx wrangler secret put OPENAI_API_KEY
OPENAI_API_KEY=

# NOTE: NEXT_PUBLIC_* vars are inlined at BUILD time, not read at runtime.
# Set those in `.env.local` (for `next dev`/`next build`) — not here.
